sRide captures the following information from the users though the website usage to ensure a quality service of the sRide carpool solution. The data points mentioned here are an indication of the type of data captured and are not limited to the ones mentioned here.
Registration details – Only to contact the user based on his approval to be contacted such as Name, phone number, email etc
