sRide captures the following information from the users though the Mobile app usage to ensure a quality service of the sRide carpool solution. The data points mentioned here are an indication of the type of data captured and are not limited to the ones mentioned here.
Mandatory:
Name / Gender / Email / Phone number/ user type / car details / OS details ad version
Optional:
