Changes to our Privacy Policy:
If at any point we decide to use particular personally identifiable information in a manner materially different from that stated at the time it was collected, we will notify you by way of an email or by providing 20 days notice on the sRide Mobile Platform. We also encourage you to review this privacy policy periodically.
Contacting sRide:
If you have any questions about this privacy statement contact us at support@sride.co.
Amendments and Updates:
This Privacy Policy may be updated, amended, and revised from time to time and all users of sRide’s services will have an opportunity to review any updated, amended, and/or revised Privacy Policy and whether or not you have reviewed any updated, amended, and/or revised Privacy Policy, by continuing to maintain an account with sRide you consent to the terms and provisions contained in any Privacy Policy utilized by sRide.
